        "prompt": "=Using the daily business status: {{$json.data}} \n\nCreate a brief, high-energy Telegram brief for the business owner.\n\nStructure:\n1. 💵 Estimated Daily Cash Flow Target\n2. ⚡ Top 3 Critical Revenue Actions for Today (who to call/email/follow up, and expected outcomes)\n3. ⚠️ Critical Risks (outstanding invoices, stalled deals)\n\nKeep it short and formatted in bold markdown for Telegram reading.",
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "8fdfd422-e1d9-482a-a9fa-a9f81a7d6e7b",
      "name": "Draft Daily Revenue Brief",
